(numIntPhysRegisters, nICacheWays).explanation: The number of integer physical registers and instruction cache associativity are independent architectural parameters that serve different functions in the processor pipeline;

(numIntPhysRegisters, power_internal).explanation: Increasing the number of integer physical registers directly increases internal power consumption due to additional register file circuitry and access operations;

(numIntPhysRegisters, area_net_area).explanation: More integer physical registers require additional interconnect routing between registers and functional units, directly increasing the net area for wiring;
